    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/a9bd78c5d0c66a1088d18d73d7c245f3.poster.avif?t=1749045761\" width=600 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/a9bd78c5d0c66a1088d18d73d7c245f3.webm?t=1749045761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/a9bd78c5d0c66a1088d18d73d7c245f3.mp4?t=1749045761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>将平台游戏带到天堂高度！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身有史以来最快的光环！在这款独特的基于物理的平台游戏中，加入莱米拉和莱利斯高速远征，从恶魔手中夺回家园。掌握精准移动的技巧，在流畅灵敏的操控下，冲刺、弹跳、翱翔于专为挑战超音速而设计的关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/a458a728a524d88de0a817bf98eeb873.poster.avif?t=1749045761\" width=600 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/a458a728a524d88de0a817bf98eeb873.webm?t=1749045761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/a458a728a524d88de0a817bf98eeb873.mp4?t=1749045761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>从恶魔王手中拯救你的家园</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在恶魔被驱逐数百年后，天国再度面临危机。恶魔大军在自称魔王的拉泽尔领导下卷土重来，企图彻底占领天使的国度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/74e0814d668b263cfa10fe8c2dc8744d.poster.avif?t=1749045761\" width=600 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/74e0814d668b263cfa10fe8c2dc8744d.webm?t=1749045761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/74e0814d668b263cfa10fe8c2dc8744d.mp4?t=1749045761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索独特又充满活力的多种生态，发现不断拓展的玩法与机制。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>易于上手，精通后乐趣无穷。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>节奏明快的原声音乐，为你的速度注入动力。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>攀登全球排行榜，超越极限。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发掘隐藏的收集品。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/c235197fdb6bc7bf44898eab7b9cac04.poster.avif?t=1749045761\" width=600 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/c235197fdb6bc7bf44898eab7b9cac04.webm?t=1749045761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387460/extras/c235197fdb6bc7bf44898eab7b9cac04.mp4?t=1749045761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
